        <abstract>
            <p>His satisfaction at CD’s acceptance of book as well as total public acceptance. Murray has given him a £250 advance. His pleasure at Asa Gray’s words.</p>
            <p>Next task will be to write on origin [of species] by segregation of local races.</p>
        </abstract>
